>> source: https://www.bigoven.com/recipe/jamie-oliver-tomato-salad/2172710
>> total time: 45 minutes
>> serves: 1

Add @basil{1%small bunch} leaves to #blender{} with pinch of @salt{} and @paper{}, a peeled clove of @garlic{1%clove}, two logs of extra virgin @olive oil{}, and a splash of @white wine vinegar{1%splash}. Whiz until dark green oil. Taste and adjust seasoning if needed.

Halve or quarter @mixed cherry tomatoes{300%g} and poor dressing over them. Scatter with basil leaves and a pinch of salt or two.
